00:56.642 --> 01:00.187
[ Sighs ]
I'm not even
gonna say it, Kate.

01:00.270 --> 01:02.856
Then it'll be
like I never left.

01:04.607 --> 01:06.526
Okay ?

01:18.036 --> 01:20.497
Wait.

01:22.499 --> 01:25.418
I have a really bad feeling
about this.

01:25.501 --> 01:27.670
About the plane ?

01:27.754 --> 01:30.047
You think it's gonna crash ?
Don't say that.

01:30.172 --> 01:33.133
No. Look, I know that
we've talked about this
a thousand times,

01:33.259 --> 01:36.804
and we agreed that
going to London was
the right thing to do.

01:36.929 --> 01:40.640
But in my heart...
this feels wrong.

01:42.392 --> 01:45.270
Don't go, Jack.
You mean don't go at all ?

01:45.436 --> 01:47.688
Well, what--
what about my internship ?

01:47.855 --> 01:51.484
Believe me, I know--
I know what an incredible
opportunity this is for you.

01:51.650 --> 01:54.612
For us, Kate.
Right, for us.

01:54.695 --> 01:58.073
But I'm afraid that
if you get on that plane--
Look.

01:58.156 --> 02:02.410
We're at the airport.
Nobody ever thinks clearly
at the airport.

02:02.494 --> 02:05.205
So we should just trust
the decision we already made.

02:05.330 --> 02:08.916
You've been accepted
to one of the best law schools
in the country.

02:09.000 --> 02:13.629
I've got this internship
at Barclay's Bank.
We have a great plan, honey.

02:15.506 --> 02:17.758
You wanna do something
great, Jack ?

02:17.883 --> 02:22.637
Let's flush the plan.
Let's start our lives
right now, today.

02:22.762 --> 02:25.139
I mean, I have no idea
what this life is gonna
look like,

02:25.265 --> 02:29.393
but I know that it has
the both of us in it,
and I choose us.

02:32.188 --> 02:35.190
The plan doesn't
make us great, Jack.

02:35.315 --> 02:38.527
What we have together,
that's what makes us great.

02:47.869 --> 02:51.497
- I love you, Kate.
- I love you too. I do.

02:56.919 --> 03:00.464
And one year in London
is not gonna change that.

03:00.589 --> 03:03.091
A hundred years
couldn't change that.

03:22.192 --> 03:25.069
Experts are predicting
a mild rally in the bond market.

03:25.153 --> 03:28.072
[ Continues Indistinctly ]

03:35.245 --> 03:38.332
[ Woman ]
Last night was incredible.
Huh ?

03:38.457 --> 03:40.584
I said, last night was great.

03:40.667 --> 03:44.254
You are
an amazing lover.

03:44.379 --> 03:46.506
Thanks.
You're not bad yourself.

03:46.673 --> 03:50.092
- I wanna see you again.
- I'd like that too.

03:50.176 --> 03:54.388
Tonight.
It's Christmas eve, Jack.

03:54.513 --> 03:57.933
So ? I'll pour
eggnog over you.
[ Laughing ]

03:58.016 --> 04:01.686
- [ Growls ]
- I have to go visit
my parents out in Jersey.

04:01.895 --> 04:06.733
Jersey ? Do you have
any idea what the traffic's
gonna be like ?

04:06.858 --> 04:09.318
That's why I'm taking
the train.

04:11.112 --> 04:13.656
It was nice
meeting you, Jack.

