So, like the dress ?
Oh, it's lovely.

35:03.143 --> 35:06.646
I thought
I saw you notice it
at the kids' recital.

35:06.771 --> 35:08.981
It's lovely.
It's lovely.

35:19.574 --> 35:21.451
There he is.

35:21.576 --> 35:24.746
Hey, Jack.
Happy holidays, man.
Yeah.

35:26.164 --> 35:28.374
Jack, come on over.

35:31.836 --> 35:34.880
Hey, Jack.
Cheers, baby.

35:34.963 --> 35:38.050
You guys see Van Horn
last night ?
Thirty-two points.

35:38.175 --> 35:41.553
That kid's gonna take
the Nets to the championship.
The Nets ? Are you kidding ?

35:41.636 --> 35:43.555
They suck.

35:46.474 --> 35:49.477
But they're due.
They're certainly due.

35:49.602 --> 35:52.396
So, tomorrow's
the big day, Jackie.

35:52.521 --> 35:55.274
Okay. Why ?

35:55.357 --> 35:57.943
My triple bypass.

35:58.026 --> 36:00.612
I'm going
under the knife tomorrow.
I told you that, right ?

36:00.737 --> 36:02.614
Triple bypass.
Yeah.

36:02.739 --> 36:05.158
You really think you
should be eating all that ?
Eh.

36:05.325 --> 36:07.160
Figure I'm going in
for a cleaning tomorrow.

36:07.326 --> 36:09.412
Might as well load up
on the fried stuff tonight,
right ?

36:09.495 --> 36:11.997
That's good thinking, Bill.
Have another drink.

36:12.123 --> 36:16.418
Some fried pork,
mashed potatoes.
He'll be dead by morning.

36:16.543 --> 36:19.504
- How 'bout a cigar, Jack ?
- Oh, no, thank you.
I'm cutting down.

36:19.588 --> 36:22.424
- Come on. They're
American made, not Cuban.
- Oh, really ?

36:22.549 --> 36:24.092
Come on.

36:26.594 --> 36:28.763
Very nice.
I thought you'd like 'em.

36:30.723 --> 36:33.142
Mm. Mmm !

36:33.225 --> 36:35.144
Superb.

36:35.227 --> 36:37.896
How 'bout you, Arnie ?
I'm all right. Thanks.

36:39.481 --> 36:42.108
Finger food ?
No, thank you.
I'm fine.

36:42.192 --> 36:44.861
Come on.
Soon as I put 'em down,
you're gonna grab a couple.

36:45.028 --> 36:46.988
You always do.
No, I'm okay.

36:47.113 --> 36:49.782
Let me. They will melt
in your mouth.

36:49.907 --> 36:52.451
Yeah.

36:55.913 --> 36:59.583
Good ?
Fabulous.

36:59.666 --> 37:04.337
At the end of this whole thing,
she made me this
hand-embroidered sweater.

37:04.420 --> 37:06.422
It was really lovely.
[ Jeannie ]
How nice.

37:06.506 --> 37:09.967
So I'm slipping it on and
I notice that she's misspelled
the word "lawyers. "

37:10.092 --> 37:13.804
Uh-oh.
I spent the entire day
walking around...

37:13.887 --> 37:17.766
with a sweater that said,
" Nonprofit layers
do it for free."

37:21.144 --> 37:23.271
So you're a lawyer ?

37:24.772 --> 37:27.316
A nonprofit lawyer ?

37:27.442 --> 37:29.652
Probono.

37:29.777 --> 37:33.113
