Nobody makes a dime ?
-Jack ?

37:36.992 --> 37:39.202
"Any hoo--"

37:41.079 --> 37:42.956
[ Barks ]

37:43.081 --> 37:45.291
[ Growling ]

37:49.420 --> 37:52.381
I better go wake my mom.
There you go.

37:52.464 --> 37:54.383
Uh, I don't think so.

37:54.466 --> 37:57.552
- She's your dog, Jack.
- No, she's not.

37:57.678 --> 38:00.013
You're right.
She's the kids' dog.

38:00.138 --> 38:03.808
Maybe we should go wake Josh
and make him walk her.
[ Chuckles ]

38:11.315 --> 38:16.028
If you take a dump sometime
in this century, then we could
go home where it's warm.

38:17.821 --> 38:20.490
If I can even remember
how to get home.

38:20.657 --> 38:22.867
You remember,
don't you, girl ?

