[ Coos ]

41:15.943 --> 41:18.278
You're not really
my dad, are you ?

41:22.407 --> 41:24.450
No, I'm not.

41:24.576 --> 41:28.329
I work on Wall Street,
you know, with
the big buildings.

41:28.454 --> 41:30.873
I live in an apartment
with a doorman.

41:31.040 --> 41:33.667
And I can buy
almost anything I want.

41:33.751 --> 41:36.461
This isn't my life.
It's just a glimpse.

41:37.838 --> 41:39.798
Where's my real dad ?

41:42.384 --> 41:44.761
I don't know.
But don't worry.

41:44.844 --> 41:48.556
He loves you, and I'm sure
he'll be back very soon.

42:14.038 --> 42:16.498
What are you doing ?

42:27.383 --> 42:30.094
They did a pretty good job.

42:30.177 --> 42:31.637
Who did ?

42:31.804 --> 42:34.682
The aliens
in the mother ship.

42:34.807 --> 42:36.683
You look just like him.

42:36.808 --> 42:39.644
Oh, thanks.

42:39.728 --> 42:42.230
Slightly better looking
though, right ?

42:45.149 --> 42:47.985
Oh, no, you're not gonna
start crying, are you ?

42:48.110 --> 42:51.238
I don't think I could
really deal with that right now.

42:53.240 --> 42:55.492
Do you like kids ?

42:56.702 --> 42:58.745
On a case by case basis.

43:00.163 --> 43:02.582
Do you know how
to make chocolate milk ?

43:04.626 --> 43:07.086
I--I think I could
figure it out.

43:07.170 --> 43:10.756
Promise you won't kidnap
me and my brother...

43:10.923 --> 43:13.175
and plant stuff
in our brains ?

43:13.259 --> 43:14.927
Sure.

43:21.600 --> 43:24.561
Welcome to Earth.

