in there, sweetheart.

01:13:52.945 --> 01:13:55.322
Mm, not bad.
Good.

01:13:55.405 --> 01:13:57.324
I should have warned you.

01:13:57.407 --> 01:14:01.369
Dad always does
something really special
for the anniversary.

01:14:01.494 --> 01:14:05.123
Like what ?
